WEBVTT

00:00.125 --> 00:03.145
- <i>Previously, on</i> Good Witch:
- Movies at the old Middleton Theatre

00:03.170 --> 00:05.337
- again? That's a great idea!
- And they want me to

00:05.372 --> 00:06.300
invest in it with them.

00:06.325 --> 00:09.508
If I listen to people more,
I might get more of what I want.

00:09.543 --> 00:11.845
I wanted you to know
how much I care about you.

00:18.152 --> 00:21.853
You were so certain you were right!

00:23.724 --> 00:25.791
I had tried the combination
a dozen times!

00:25.826 --> 00:28.060
Hmm. Well, it's a good thing
you tried a thirteenth.

00:28.095 --> 00:31.697
Well, which allowed you to be
right. But I'm glad you were.

00:31.732 --> 00:33.965
No, I wasn't trying to be
right, I was trying to be nice.

00:34.001 --> 00:36.535
See, I didn't want you standing
outside your door in the cold

00:36.570 --> 00:38.637
on your first night here.

00:38.672 --> 00:41.673
I never even imagined
meeting a neighbor like you.

00:43.210 --> 00:45.177
I can't imagine living
next door to anyone else.

00:45.212 --> 00:48.407
Almost makes a guy believe in fate.

00:49.183 --> 00:51.683
- I said, "almost."
- See, that's what I love

00:51.719 --> 00:53.919
about you. You never take
anything at face value.

00:53.954 --> 00:56.188
You wait 'til you're absolutely
certain something is true

00:56.223 --> 00:59.391
before you say it, which is why it
means so much more when you do.

00:59.426 --> 01:01.259
Hm. Well,

01:01.295 --> 01:03.338
here's something that's true.

01:05.048 --> 01:07.566
You changed everything for me.

01:08.552 --> 01:12.504
And I hardly remember how we got
here. But I am glad we did.

01:13.265 --> 01:16.074
I can't wait to see where we go next.

01:24.218 --> 01:26.284
And I want to say one more thing.

01:26.320 --> 01:27.946
Yeah?

01:29.490 --> 01:32.090
How could you possibly have known

01:32.126 --> 01:34.092
that that key box
would open the last time?

01:34.128 --> 01:36.895
- Let it go, Sam.
- It's going to bug me forever.

01:36.930 --> 01:39.898
Well, maybe that's why I did it.

